442
00:28:21,406 --> 00:28:25,399
Gospodine Finley, Dr. Kearns,
molim vas pridjite.

443
00:28:26,644 --> 00:28:29,698
Gradjanska parnica, Robert kearns protiv kompanije Ford Motor

